OL,3,CBoris Bus and Gherkin designers among
OL,4,Cshortlist for Queen Elizabeth II
OL,5,Cmemorial
OL,7,FThe design teams behind London's Boris
OL,8,FBuses, the 2012 Olympic cauldron and
OL,9,F30 St Mary's Axe - known as The
OL,10,FGherkin - have made it to a shortlist
OL,11,Fof five to create a memorial in
OL,12,Fcentral London for Queen Elizabeth II.
OL,14,FDesigners from across the UK submitted
OL,15,Ftheir concepts for the first stage of
OL,16,Fthe process and the winner is due to
OL,17,Fbe announced in the summer.
