OL,7,FThe site for the new national Queen
OL,8,FElizabeth II Memorial will include the
OL,9,Farea of St James's Park adjacent to
OL,10,FThe Mall at Marlborough Gate and land
OL,11,Fsurrounding the pathway down to the
OL,12,Flake, including the Blue Bridge.
OL,14,FThe area was chosen because of its
OL,15,Fproximity to the ceremonial route of
OL,16,FThe Mall, its historical and
OL,17,Fconstitutional significance and
OL,18,Fpersonal connection to Queen Elizabeth.
OL,20,FIn full the shortlist is:
