OL,5,Cmemorial
OL,7,FThe final design will be formally
OL,8,Fannounced in April 2026, to coincide
OL,9,Fwith what would have been Queen
OL,10,FElizabeth's hundredth birthday year.
OL,12,FA Cabinet Office statement added: "The
OL,13,Ffinalists were shortlisted following
OL,14,Fthe first stage of a two-stage open
OL,15,Fcompetition. Designers were required
OL,16,Fto submit examples of previous
OL,17,Fprojects relevant to the vision for
OL,18,Fthe memorial set out by the Queen
OL,19,FElizabeth Memorial Committee,
OL,20,Falongside details of the unique skills
OL,21,Fof their multi-disciplinary teams.
