OL,3,CBoris Bus and Gherkin designers among
OL,4,Cshortlist for Queen Elizabeth II
OL,5,Cmemorial
OL,7,F"The winning design team will be
OL,8,Fannounced in Summer 2025 after the
OL,9,FSelection Panel reviews the five
OL,10,Fshortlisted teams' concepts. Design
OL,11,Fteams have been asked to create a
OL,12,Fmemorial masterplan that celebrates
OL,13,FQueen Elizabeth II's extraordinary
OL,14,Flife of service and provides a space
OL,15,Ffor pause and reflection.
OL,17,F"The designs will also be assessed
OL,18,Fagainst wider criteria, including
OL,19,Fvalue for money, placemaking and
OL,20,Fvisitor experience."
